#: index.php:384
msgid "Donations"
msgstr "Rhoddion"

#: index.php:385
msgid ""
"Since I'm getting asked about this on regular basis, there is <b>no</b> "
"donation button on this page."
msgstr ""
"Ers i mi gael fy holi ynglŷn â hyn yn rheolaidd, nid oes botwm rhoi <b>dim</"
"b> ar y dudalen hon."

#: index.php:386
msgid ""
"The main reason is that I feel that the donation system doesn't actually "
"help software development and worse, can be guilt-inducing for users who "
"choose not to donate."
msgstr ""
"Y prif reswm yw fy mod i'n teimlo nad yw'r system rhoi yn helpu datblygiad "
"meddalwedd ac yn waeth, gall beri euogrwydd i ddefnyddwyr sy'n dewis peidio "
"â rhoi."

#: index.php:389
#, php-format
msgid ""
"If you really insist, you can always make a donation to the <a target="
"\"_blank\" %s>Free Software Foundation</a>, as they are the main reason "
"software like Rufus is possible."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi wir yn mynnu, gallwch chi bob amser roi rhodd i'r <a target="
"\"_blank\" %s>Free Software Foundation</a>, gan mai nhw yw'r prif reswm mae "
"meddalwedd fel Rufus yn bosibl."

#: index.php:390
msgid ""
"At any rate, I'll take this opportunity to say <i><u>thank you</u></i> for "
"your continuing support and enthusiasm about this little program: it is much "
"appreciated!"
msgstr ""
"Ar unrhyw gyfradd, cymeraf y cyfle hwn i ddweud <i><u>diolch</u></i> am eich "
"cefnogaeth a'ch brwdfrydedd parhaus am y rhaglen fach hon: gwerthfawrogir yn "
"fawr!"

#: index.php:391
msgid ""
"But please continue to feel free to use Rufus without any guilt about not "
"contributing for it financially &ndash; you should never have to!"
msgstr ""
"Ond parhewch i deimlo'n rhydd i ddefnyddio Rufus heb unrhyw euogrwydd am "
"beidio â chyfrannu amdano'n ariannol &ndash; ni ddylech fyth orfod!"

